Epilogue

[Trixie]

Snips discovered Trixal's body during the cleanup. Then he discovered that Trixal was Trixie all along. Snips mourned Trixie's passing for months.

Trixie was the first fem awarded the Golden Leathergnome, the highest combat medal in the land.

[

[Hazmat]

General Hazmat was shunned by gnomes. Exiled, he wandered from bigs town to bigs town, finally winding up in a land of giants where he found work in a tavern where he passed away in a tragic accident. While trying to clean a spittoon, he slip, flell in and drowned.
